Text: i downloaded this nd everytme i go to play it on my ps3 it says "corrupt data"? and idk why ?. it plays im bros windows 7 computer. but not on mine ..

My old PSP would do that too with certain MP4 files so to get them to work I would just re-convert them using VisualHub, but I use a Mac, and i dont know if it has a windows version. Just look for a program that converts video files to PSP format, and re-convert it. Hope that helps :)
